"We're on Earth," Empath explains, "In the distant past.  Our group 
has been marooned here by a time-travelling accident, and now we're 
probably going to be pulled into the war that's going on between 
several other groups of transformers that also ended up here, by 
various routes."  She transforms to robot mode and gestures.  "Shall 
we go inside?"
